WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.520 --> 00:00:01.600
Good morning family.

00:00:01.600 --> 00:00:02.649
Praise the Lord.

00:00:02.649 --> 00:00:04.621
Well, I'm back in my spot.

00:00:04.621 --> 00:00:08.112
I like to come over here; I like this artwork behind us.

00:00:08.112 --> 00:00:09.340
It's something different.

00:00:09.640 --> 00:00:15.744
We do the green screen so much, and Braden said, "Let's do a video today.

00:00:16.352 --> 00:00:16.960
" Yeah.

00:00:16.960 --> 00:00:23.119
So, I'm going to go over some of the things that the Lord gave us yesterday.

00:00:23.119 --> 00:00:26.987
For the ones that didn't watch all the prayer video, I saw a cone.

00:00:26.987 --> 00:00:30.062
It went down like a funnel.

00:00:30.790 --> 00:00:34.000
And at the base of the cone, there was gold.

00:00:34.300 --> 00:00:38.719
There were roads all around it going to the base.

00:00:38.719 --> 00:00:54.276
And there were 18-wheeler rigs that were bringing gold—pure, almost translucent gold—to the bottom of this cone.

00:00:55.093 --> 00:01:03.006
It had a hole in the middle of it like a donut, but it was thick because the semis were bringing this gold.

00:01:03.383 --> 00:01:11.725
It looked identical to the streets of gold in heaven, the translucence of the gold.

00:01:15.634 --> 00:01:24.500
So, they were taking this gold-like cement and these trucks were dumping it into a round circle.

00:01:24.880 --> 00:01:29.813
As they were moving down, they were dumping the gold, and the gold was getting thicker and thicker.

00:01:31.500 --> 00:01:38.755
I could see the thickness of the gold and a hole in the middle.

00:01:38.755 --> 00:01:41.463
Now, nothing was going through that hole.

00:01:41.463 --> 00:01:50.320
I don't know why the hole was there, but it looked like a black hole and it was completely dark all the way through.

00:01:50.320 --> 00:01:53.968
So, there was nothing coming up and nothing going down, but it was a cone.

00:01:54.216 --> 00:02:01.759
I could see the cone shape; it wasn't like a cylinder cone.

00:02:01.759 --> 00:02:04.210
It was like a square-looking cone.

00:02:04.754 --> 00:02:05.726
I thought that was interesting.

00:02:05.726 --> 00:02:21.920
It had four sides at the top and it went around all the way up, and it was a cylinder at the bottom and then went up like a square at the top, kind of like a castle, which was very interesting because it did not go all the way up like that.

00:02:21.920 --> 00:02:31.467
But these semis had silver beds with white tarps over the top of them to hide the gold.

00:02:32.660 --> 00:02:41.348
The semis had red grills on the front and they were silver semis with red grills and red front plates, which I thought was interesting.

00:02:44.046 --> 00:02:49.387
I try to tell you more detail as the day goes, as I'm re-going over the things and telling y'all.

00:02:56.235 --> 00:02:58.845
That was part of the vision.

00:02:58.845 --> 00:03:05.570
Then I saw Ronald Reagan's face before me.

00:03:06.800 --> 00:03:18.000
And I saw the old Soviet Union, the old flag that looked like an anchor with the red and all that for the old Soviet Union.

00:03:20.779 --> 00:03:22.593
I could see it in the background.

00:03:22.593 --> 00:03:24.766
I could see the wall, the Berlin wall.

00:03:26.649 --> 00:03:26.939
"Bring down that wall, Gorbachev!

00:03:28.319 --> 00:03:33.540
" I could see the wall and I could see Ronald Reagan's face.

00:03:33.540 --> 00:03:38.650
But Trump's face connected to Ronald Reagan's face.

00:03:38.650 --> 00:03:43.556
So, it was half of Ronald Reagan's face and half of Trump's face.

00:03:43.556 --> 00:03:53.524
And as they moved, it was like as Ronald Reagan's face kind of faded in the background, Trump's face came to the forefront.

00:03:53.809 --> 00:03:56.231
I could see his hair and his eyes.

00:03:56.408 --> 00:04:00.827
He had the blue suit on with the white shirt and the red tie, just like he always does.

00:04:01.111 --> 00:04:03.439
It was there and I could see it.

00:04:03.439 --> 00:04:17.879
But then this is what's interesting: I could see the writing on a wall again behind Trump that looked like graffiti.

00:04:20.479 --> 00:04:25.691
It was graffiti with bubble letters, and it looked like somebody had really messed up the wall behind him.

00:04:26.520 --> 00:04:32.320
But it was puffy, bold letters in different fonts.

00:04:33.279 --> 00:04:41.209
It was behind him, but I couldn't make out what the bubble letters said; I could see them behind him, kind of like gang writing.

00:04:43.740 --> 00:04:57.645
And so then I saw the design like whenever you see the old Batman things like "pow," "boom," "bang," and they would have the explosion design and the words there whenever they were fighting.

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:11.049
I saw that design and I heard "Golden Age" as I saw Trump's face.

00:05:11.049 --> 00:05:12.689
I heard "Golden Age.

00:05:12.689 --> 00:05:14.719
" And the Lord corrected me.

00:05:14.719 --> 00:05:20.196
He said, "Stop always thinking you know how big the window truly is.

00:05:20.196 --> 00:05:32.000
For I want to make this a reward of the wealth of the sinner laid up for the righteous and for you to enjoy the wealth that you're about to receive.

00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:47.874
" He said, "Brandon, this is a wealth transfer for the remnant—the ones that have listened to me and have sacrificially given and sacrificially done the things that I've called you to do without compromise.

00:05:47.874 --> 00:05:50.645
You have been right on.

00:05:50.645 --> 00:05:55.236
And I am your exceedingly great reward.

00:05:55.236 --> 00:06:01.349
I am the El Shaddai, the all-sufficient one.

00:06:01.349 --> 00:06:03.580
I supply all your needs.

00:06:03.580 --> 00:06:04.390
Do you understand?

00:06:04.390 --> 00:06:07.024
" God is a God that has an abundant supply.

00:06:07.024 --> 00:06:10.107
Ladies and gentlemen, God is not a poor God.

00:06:10.107 --> 00:06:15.890
If you like poverty, you're certainly not going to like heaven.

00:06:15.890 --> 00:06:17.760
There is no poverty in heaven.

00:06:17.760 --> 00:06:20.069
There are streets paved with gold.

00:06:20.069 --> 00:06:27.691
The foundation has rubies, diamonds, sapphires, and all the beautiful stones that you could ever imagine.

00:06:27.691 --> 00:06:29.420
Folks, I have seen these visions.

00:06:29.420 --> 00:06:34.160
I have seen what God has prepared for the body of Christ.

00:06:34.160 --> 00:06:42.140
If you, being evil, give good gifts to your children, how much more does your heavenly Father give good gifts to those that love him?

00:06:42.140 --> 00:06:48.680
And I'm telling you, ladies and gentlemen, God has more than enough for you and what's about to happen and a Golden Age.

00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:59.360
He said, "A Golden Age," and I saw a calendar again and a season of blessing for the body of Christ.

00:06:59.360 --> 00:07:03.417
Now, you say, "Well, Brandon, your words kind of contradict each other.

00:07:03.417 --> 00:07:05.177
You said you saw a crash.

00:07:06.720 --> 00:07:08.320
" Yes, I have.

00:07:09.920 --> 00:07:19.526
But just like words are given to an audience, what is the time frame that it's supposed to take place?

00:07:19.526 --> 00:07:30.258
Just like Jeremiah and Daniel, the word that Daniel gave has still not come to pass.

00:07:30.258 --> 00:07:40.159
And all the way to John, the same words did not come to pass there; we're seeing them manifest thousands of years later.

00:07:49.736 --> 00:07:52.059
And the Lord told me, "Stop trying to control the time frame, trying to reason it in your mind of when you think these things are going to take place.

00:07:52.059 --> 00:07:54.091
" He's coming, ladies and gentlemen.

00:07:54.091 --> 00:08:07.360
But just like I told you, it has to come through the vessel, speaking it out into existence into the atmosphere, just like the prophets did before Jesus came the first time.

00:08:21.051 --> 00:08:31.248
He said, "Brandon, I'm going to raise up these words coming up out of you, for I am decreeing this through you.

00:08:46.760 --> 00:08:46.960
You are my voice.

00:08:46.960 --> 00:08:48.080
Peace in this earth.

00:08:48.080 --> 00:08:50.869
" That's why he's saying, "Have a backbone.

00:08:50.869 --> 00:08:54.240
Say what I say to say and walk away from it.

00:08:54.240 --> 00:09:05.279
" Decree and declare the words that I'm giving you to tell the people that I'm coming, that the sun is setting on the horizon of time and you have a window.

00:09:05.279 --> 00:09:30.293
Trying to figure out God's timing whenever a thousand years is a day and a day is a thousand years to the Lord is pretty ignorant, basically, when we try to put it in our thinking and go, "Well, God's saying this and God's saying that," unless he gives me a specific saying, well, "Thus saith the Lord, it's coming on this day at this hour and this time.

00:09:30.293 --> 00:09:36.800
" Usually, he has never done that to me; it's usually very broad: this is what's coming.

00:09:37.520 --> 00:09:42.680
And you know, it's the same thing whenever I gave the word about Trump's ear.

00:09:59.289 --> 00:09:59.659
I had no idea when that was going to manifest.

00:10:01.769 --> 00:10:02.880
I just saw all that I saw and I told y'all.

00:10:02.880 --> 00:10:15.416
I tried to think that it was going to happen in the summer months, and it did, because I saw the green grass and the green trees.

00:10:15.416 --> 00:10:24.857
I saw all those things, so I knew it wasn't going to come in the winter because of the fact that there's green grass and green trees.

00:10:24.857 --> 00:10:42.090
Same thing about the woman that I saw: she had the French twist in her hair, she has a ballroom gown, and it will be at his Mar-al-lago that this lady tries to come in there looking beautiful.

00:10:42.090 --> 00:10:45.626
She looked like a supermodel and she was young.

00:10:45.626 --> 00:10:51.671
She walked up to him and she was point-blank at his chest.

00:10:51.671 --> 00:10:57.700
This lady was coming underneath the radar because she was gorgeous.

00:10:57.700 --> 00:10:59.200
Now, why?

00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:01.288
I have no idea.

00:11:19.406 --> 00:11:19.749
This is the vision that I saw, and I've already warned about this several times.

00:11:25.120 --> 00:11:35.680
The Lord told me there will be attempts on his life in the future—that this is not over and that we are to pray over him continually because of what his position holds and what God has in store for him.

00:11:35.680 --> 00:11:40.578
It is not for him to be taken out by any foreign adversary.

00:11:40.578 --> 00:11:41.733
Do you understand?

00:11:41.733 --> 00:11:50.165
Our job is to always pray protection over every political leader and ask God to intervene and protect.

00:11:53.680 --> 00:11:56.150
The Lord told me a major crash was coming to the Chinese economy.

00:11:56.150 --> 00:12:04.920
We see this; He warned me about a window that looked like an open stage curtain.

00:12:13.390 --> 00:12:21.040
You know, whenever you see those stage curtains with the thick tapestry, the drapes—the thick drapes—but it was a red and yellow-gold drape that was just like their flag.

00:12:21.040 --> 00:12:39.312
There were red drapes and gold tassels coming down, and there was a golden rope tied in the center for the drapes of the stage of the show, like you would see at a big theater.

00:12:49.376 --> 00:12:50.010
It was opened like this, like you're peeking out of it.

00:13:04.189 --> 00:13:04.516
It was opened, and it opened up pretty wide, but the drapes at the top were touching and the drapes at the bottom were touching.

00:13:04.516 --> 00:13:07.404
All that was open was in the middle.

00:13:14.240 --> 00:13:15.920
I usually don't go into this kind of detail whenever I talk because I try to save you all time, but this is what I saw.

00:13:15.920 --> 00:13:39.486
I saw the drape, and the Lord said there was an opening coming for the body of Christ when this economy shakes, and there will be uprising and rioting and things happening in the Chinese community and all of China, rising to overthrow the government.

00:13:49.840 --> 00:13:50.240
In this window, I will give you an opportunity for the gospel to be preached in all of China, for there will be distractions.

00:13:50.240 --> 00:13:51.497
You understand?

00:13:51.497 --> 00:13:57.067
With all the economy stuff, there are distractions.

00:14:12.160 --> 00:14:12.460
So, people can come through that window and minister the gospel, but it wasn't very big and it didn't last a long time.

00:14:12.460 --> 00:14:18.426
This would be the same thing that happens with North Korea—the same things.

00:14:24.720 --> 00:14:24.942
Do you understand?

00:14:27.406 --> 00:14:29.120
And then remember what I warned you about: a Pearl Harbor experience.

00:14:45.297 --> 00:14:45.635
As the Chinese become desperate like a dog in a corner, they try to retaliate because it's insulting to their culture.

00:14:45.635 --> 00:14:47.324
Does that make sense?

00:14:47.324 --> 00:14:48.427
They felt dishonored.

00:14:48.427 --> 00:14:51.707
They felt embarrassed because of all that was going around in the culture.

00:14:51.707 --> 00:14:58.160
I don't know how else to describe it to you, and that's why I'm trying to rehearse this so you know what I've seen.

00:14:58.160 --> 00:15:01.508
It's getting ready to happen soon; I feel it inside.

00:15:01.508 --> 00:15:10.079
Things like this are escalating on a greater scale, and you will see in the days ahead a major shaking in the economy of China.

00:15:10.079 --> 00:15:20.053
Yeah, the Lord warned me about that three-month window about the tariffs to pray over the releasing of an agreement—a peace agreement—a compromise with the trade war.

00:15:23.879 --> 00:15:27.606
I saw the shelves still empty, and the Lord has warned me about shelves being empty in certain cities for sure.

00:15:27.606 --> 00:15:51.864
There, like Costcos, Walmarts, Targets, and Sam's Supercenters, they would not have enough merchandise in the days ahead for all of the shelves; they would have to take one store and put that merchandise in another store to have one location in some cities.

00:15:51.864 --> 00:16:06.879
In some cities, it got so bad that they had armed guards in those towns and in those cities because people were looting, trying to steal in the stores.

00:16:06.879 --> 00:16:09.040
Will we see that?

00:16:09.040 --> 00:16:10.480
I pray we do not.

00:16:10.480 --> 00:16:22.285
I pray we can avert these things through prayer and stop these things from taking place, even with the medications and things like that.

00:16:28.480 --> 00:16:32.120
The plan of the enemy, folks, is to kill, steal, and destroy, but God has come that we might have life and life more abundantly.

00:16:32.120 --> 00:16:34.870
That's what we're wanting right now.

00:16:34.870 --> 00:16:38.880
That's what we pray as the body of Christ.

00:16:38.880 --> 00:16:42.480
We are the salt of this earth.

00:16:42.480 --> 00:16:46.777
We are the ones that bring the flavor.

00:16:46.777 --> 00:16:47.897
We are the anchor.

00:16:47.897 --> 00:16:49.020
We do it all.

00:16:49.829 --> 00:17:00.160
And we pray, and God did not call and say this stuff to go, 'Oh no, the sky is falling.

00:17:00.160 --> 00:17:01.773
' No, that's not what we're doing.

00:17:10.959 --> 00:17:12.160
We're here to set a standard and pray a wall against the enemy, saying, 'Thus far, Satan, and no further.

00:17:12.160 --> 00:17:34.335
' Some of it is going to happen, but I believe that we have power and authority as the believer to tread on serpents and scorpions and nothing shall by any means hurt us.

00:17:34.335 --> 00:17:40.639
We have power to stop some of this stuff.

00:17:41.988 --> 00:17:42.582
I believe it.

00:17:42.582 --> 00:17:48.353
I want you to believe it with me because it's the truth.

00:17:48.353 --> 00:17:51.520
God gave us authority.

00:18:04.297 --> 00:18:04.594
And so then, this is the last thing: I saw Venezuela being angry about something that Trump does.

00:18:04.594 --> 00:18:10.541
Now, I do not know what that is, but something happens with Venezuela in the days ahead.

00:18:10.790 --> 00:18:12.300
It's something to do with oil.

00:18:13.337 --> 00:18:18.816
I saw them becoming angry, and Russia—I saw Putin's face coming to comfort the Venezuelan government.

00:18:18.816 --> 00:18:23.519
'Oh poor you,' you know, like, 'Oh, bless your heart, let us help you out.

00:18:23.519 --> 00:18:27.063
' That's the only way to describe it.

00:18:27.063 --> 00:18:31.440
It wasn't like that, but it's like, 'Oh, bless your heart, let us help you out.

00:18:32.160 --> 00:18:32.880
You join up with us.

00:18:36.195 --> 00:18:42.575
You become friends with us under the table right now.

00:18:42.960 --> 00:18:44.011
We have a plan.

00:18:44.011 --> 00:18:48.389
' Remember what I'm telling you: 'We have a plan, Venezuela.

00:18:48.389 --> 00:18:59.089
We can't come out with it all the way right now, but we have a plan to overdominate the dollar in the Western culture.

00:18:59.089 --> 00:19:04.680
You come in with us and we'll rescue you.

00:19:04.680 --> 00:19:13.680
We'll be a friend when nobody else is a friend to you.

00:19:13.680 --> 00:19:23.973
' And I saw Venezuela secretly with tunnels, whatever it was, trying to talk, trying to make deals, trying to be friends.

00:19:33.547 --> 00:19:34.213
And it was the same thing with Cuba, North Korea, and Iran.

00:19:49.965 --> 00:19:50.270
In the days ahead, you'll see more Iran and Russia doing things, Turkey doing things, and you'll see an uprising in the Middle East like we've never seen before.

00:19:50.270 --> 00:19:56.516
Remember this: we're about to see great things in the Middle East.

00:19:57.138 --> 00:20:02.670
And people say, 'How are we going to have this with Israel and all this?

00:20:02.670 --> 00:20:05.620
' I saw black swan events.

00:20:05.620 --> 00:20:10.520
Black swan events with Israel and Iran trying to poke it.

00:20:10.520 --> 00:20:15.160
I'm not going to touch that anymore; I feel instant caution.

00:20:15.160 --> 00:20:20.370
You all just need to be watching in the days ahead.

00:20:20.370 --> 00:20:26.827
An escalation of war, an escalation of strikes against Iran in the days ahead.

00:20:26.827 --> 00:20:28.000
Watch these things.

00:20:28.000 --> 00:20:29.840
Consider the cost.

00:20:29.840 --> 00:20:31.964
Israel, consider the cost.

00:20:31.964 --> 00:20:35.467
So, basically, that's what I want to tell you all today.

00:20:35.467 --> 00:20:37.147
That's the highlights of yesterday's prayer.

00:20:37.147 --> 00:20:39.840
I thought it was important to always do these like this.

00:20:54.869 --> 00:20:55.179
I know it's kind of different, but I thought, 'Why not?

00:20:55.179 --> 00:21:09.966
' because I know not everybody stays for the whole prayer video, but I'll bring up what I told you all, and if you feel led to pray over these things, you can pray over them again, knowing that the time is short.

00:21:09.966 --> 00:21:13.653
How short the time is, I have no idea, ladies and gentlemen.

00:21:13.653 --> 00:21:20.009
All I know is I have an urgency to tell you all the time that Jesus Christ is coming.

00:21:20.827 --> 00:21:28.720
And He said, 'I want to give you a window of blessing, a golden age, a golden time frame for the body of Christ.

00:21:28.720 --> 00:21:32.799
' Now, are we going to see the economy falter eventually?

00:21:32.799 --> 00:21:33.394
Yes.

00:21:33.394 --> 00:21:36.160
Have I seen a major plague coming?

00:21:49.760 --> 00:21:49.920
A plague that will kill billions of people?

00:21:49.920 --> 00:21:50.240
Yes.

00:21:50.240 --> 00:21:52.663
That's like the bubonic plague—not the bubonic plague.

00:21:53.326 --> 00:21:54.789
The black plague of death.

00:21:54.789 --> 00:21:58.880
It was bad, bringing out old things through AI technology.

00:21:58.880 --> 00:22:06.960
So let's pray for tomorrow that they're going to start meeting and going about this Pope thing and this Asian man.

00:22:06.960 --> 00:22:08.239
I've seen him.

00:22:11.920 --> 00:22:14.159
I believe this is a guy over the Philippines; he looked Asian to me.

00:22:14.159 --> 00:22:22.592
Starting out good is what the Lord said—starting out good and eventually turning really bad—that it would give a window.

00:22:22.592 --> 00:22:25.349
But I saw great shaking coming to Italy.

00:22:29.703 --> 00:22:36.090
And I told you about the root busting the concrete all the way down through the Vatican, all the way down in the Vatican Square, that area.

00:22:45.893 --> 00:22:46.187
A great change, and then I saw an even darker time.

00:22:55.565 --> 00:22:55.943
I think it's interesting, even with the sky.

00:22:55.943 --> 00:22:59.253
Everybody's really interested in the sky thing.

00:22:59.253 --> 00:23:00.853
Is this a volcano thing?

00:23:00.853 --> 00:23:02.869
Is this all the folks?

00:23:02.869 --> 00:23:06.480
All I saw was that the sun was different.

00:23:06.480 --> 00:23:11.640
It looked like a haze; I don't know how else to describe it.

00:23:11.640 --> 00:23:18.742
It didn't look like a cloud per se, or like smoke; it just looked like the sun was being affected.

00:23:18.742 --> 00:23:21.307
There was something wrong with the sun.

00:23:25.520 --> 00:23:25.870
And I don't know why it would do that, but the light was weird.

00:23:25.870 --> 00:23:29.040
It was like a really weird movie.

00:23:33.333 --> 00:23:33.600
I don't know how else to describe it.

00:23:33.600 --> 00:23:37.211
I wish I could draw you a picture of it.

00:23:37.486 --> 00:23:45.600
The only way I can describe it to you is it looked like an eclipse, but it was much worse.

00:23:46.080 --> 00:23:48.502
The light was more dingy than that.

00:23:48.502 --> 00:23:50.216
All right, let's pray.

00:23:53.977 --> 00:23:54.240
I don't have anything to take communion with you all today.

00:23:54.240 --> 00:24:03.154
I'm in my car, of course, but I thought I'd pray and we'll seek the face of the Lord.

00:24:03.154 --> 00:24:06.400
I wanted to get a video out for you today.

00:24:06.400 --> 00:24:16.480
Instead of skipping today, because I had things I had to do, I thought I'd do it in the car and do something really fast for you all.

00:24:16.480 --> 00:24:23.840
We'll seek the face of the Lord real quick and if the Lord shows us anything, we'll add it to tomorrow's video.

00:24:23.840 --> 00:24:26.114
That's Megan in the background, everyone.

00:24:40.320 --> 00:24:40.600
Father, we just thank You, Lord, for another great day today.

00:24:40.600 --> 00:24:43.291
Lord, we thank You for the rain.

00:24:43.291 --> 00:24:50.693
Oklahoma is getting so much rain, Lord, and You're blessing us on so many levels with so many different rainstorms.

00:24:50.693 --> 00:24:54.960
And God, You're filling our lakes, our streams, and our creeks.

00:25:08.765 --> 00:25:08.994
Lord, You've been so good to us.

00:25:10.937 --> 00:25:12.983
